    <date day="04" month="October" year="2011"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>   A URI scheme for referencing static data abjects by means of a
   cryptographic digest mechanism is specified.  The format is designed
   to resist content type substitution attacks and supports a choice of
   digest algorithms.

	 </t>
    </abstract>
